{
  "stem": "5761.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And-- and they said, some of the families have to go along with him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we all succeeded to go along with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "15 people.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And naturally, this was our luck that he got sick, because the conditions were very bad.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We didn't have no beds, no blankets-- just freezing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only thing we kept warm, we were making, you know, fires, you know, warm up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were there for about two days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's horrible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But from there-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --we manage-- to get-- to a-- they transferred us to an area near Sverdlovsk-- big city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took us to the camps, which the camp was surrounded by barbed wire-- and told us, this is the area where you're gonna live.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There-- there were no, you know, living quarters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were no barracks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was some little homes which were not available, you know, to be rented or, you know, live there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then my father-- my family decided to build his own barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we managed to build a barrack with three rooms and a little kitchen on the side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The area was right near a big forest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This was, I remember, coldest months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they told us, here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Here are the trees.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You're welcome to go in, cut the trees, and build a house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And because of the background, you know, the lumber business, we built a house, and we lived there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We lived there over a year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they kept as-- as traitors, 'cause we refused to become Russian citizens.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they treated us as prisoners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were not allowed to get out of camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whatever we did is work.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
